(309, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wordpress.org/news/2014/03/wordpress-3-9-beta-1/'' title=''I’m excited to announce that the first beta of WordPress 3.9 is now available for testing. WordPress 3.9 is due out next month — but in order to hit that goal, we need your help testing all of the goodies we’ve added: We updated TinyMCE, the software powering the visual editor, to the latest version. […]''>WordPress 3.9 Beta 1</a> <span class="rss-date">11.03.2014</span><div class=''rssSummary''>I’m excited to announce that the first beta of WordPress 3.9 is now available for testing. WordPress 3.9 is due out next month — but in order to hit that goal, we need your help testing all of the goodies we’ve added: We updated TinyMCE, the software powering the visual editor, to the latest version. […]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wordpress.tv/2014/03/16/benjamin-beck-wordpress-seo-that-is-google-friendly/'' title=''    ''>WordPress.tv: Benjamin Beck: WordPress SEO That Is Google Friendly</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wordpress.tv/2014/03/16/andy-roberts-best-of-breed-plugins/'' title=''    ''>WordPress.tv: Andy Roberts: Best of Breed Plugins</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wordpress.tv/2014/03/16/amanda-blum-get-your-site-built-without-getting-burned/'' title=''    ''>WordPress.tv: Amanda Blum: Get Your Site Built Without Getting Burned</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Популярный плагин:</span> <a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/google-analytics-dashboard-for-wp/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Google Analytics Dashboard for WP</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=google-analytics-dashboard-for-wp&amp;_wpnonce=de8d3da8b5&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thi